{"tid":706574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大阪6.1級地震3死200傷　恐傷亡人數持續增加","createTime":"2018-06-18T04:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T05:56:30.000Z","uid":17646,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"08804909c5a9342d6a312dc8d161c10ca570de17","tid":706574,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:15:07.000Z","msg":"日本大阪周一（18日）早上發生黎克特制6.1級的淺層地震，關西多個地區都感受到強烈搖晃，暫未發出海嘯警報。有建築物搖晃超過30秒，車站內的顯示牌亦塌下，有3人死亡及逾200人受傷。大阪及鄰近兵庫縣共17萬戶停電，新幹線神戶線發出地震警戒信號，列車一度停駛。日本傳媒報道，地震中恐有多人罹難，惟消息未獲警方證實。 <br />\n<br />\n氣象廳表示，地震震源位於大阪府茨木市東南方，震源深度為10公里，屬極淺層地震。氣象廳其後把地震強度調整為6.1級，並將地震的震源的深度由10公里調整為13公里。大阪府、京都府、滋賀縣、兵庫縣、奈良縣等近畿地區分別錄得強烈震動，氣象廳警告民眾未來兩三日內須提防餘震及山泥傾瀉。據美國地質勘探局數據顯示，地震強度為5.3級，震源深度15.4公里。 <br />\n<br />\n地震發生於大阪時間早上8時（香港時間早上7時），大阪府北部高槻市有建築物起火，一名9歲女童在上學途中不幸被倒塌的泳池圍牆壓中身亡，另有一名10歲男童受傷。東淀川區一名80歲老翁被倒塌的房屋壓死，茨木市一名84歲老翁遭家中書架壓中不治。吹田市有民宅的傢具在地震中倒下，雜物散滿一地。 <br />\n<br />\n從網上影片可見，地震過後有水管爆裂，多家古建築物起火冒出白煙。關西電力表示，福井縣敦賀市的敦賀核電廠暫時沒有異樣。 <br />\n<br />\n首相安倍晉三表示，首要之務是要拯救民眾的性命，他下令官員要快速搜集損毀情況，不遺餘力搜救及向民眾提供適當的資訊。內閣官房長官菅義偉指，地震並無造成重大災害。首相官邸已經成立了緊急聯絡室，正在收集災區的情況，並聯絡自衛隊做好救災準備。"},{"pid":"3d32b54f157f174aa2b824c798bc321ca0781364","tid":706574,"uid":17646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180618/photo/bknint-20180618070013742-0618_17011_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180618%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180618070013742-0618_17011_001_01p.jpg&h=7234c197&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180618/photo/bknint-20180618070013742-0618_17011_001_02p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180618%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180618070013742-0618_17011_001_02p.jpg&h=4bb9fd52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180618/photo/bknint-20180618070013742-0618_17011_001_03p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180618%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180618070013742-0618_17011_001_03p.jpg&h=5cc2e911&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180618/photo/bknint-20180618070013742-0618_17011_001_04p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180618%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180618070013742-0618_17011_001_04p.jpg&h=38a384d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180618/photo/bknint-20180618070013742-0618_17011_001_05p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180618%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180618070013742-0618_17011_001_05p.jpg&h=2fd8909b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"291194c5c3c28e11bc41758df81bf89c5f657948","tid":706574,"uid":17646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f86ad8014df433e5e27ebc4ecc053e675727ac","tid":706574,"uid":102096,"like":5,"dislike":20,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:25:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"caa46cf9c9875ae73708a6658fef46f0442d8701","tid":706574,"uid":17646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:46:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5eff0598f6f08e378f458a29578ab10445a40c","tid":706574,"uid":186692,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:50:53.000Z","msg":"CCTVB又開盡火力講日本地震(◔౪◔)"},{"pid":"00e8d8391a7c8f0f3c2bf62e8f79a4b816c41b1d","tid":706574,"uid":176304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e9f86ad8014df433e5e27ebc4ecc053e675727ac","tid":706574,"uid":102096,"like":5,"dislike":20,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:25:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:53:12.000Z","msg":"真係唔好去"},{"pid":"79baf6fe9281f5e158b3607ad